SUPERPOWER
Apply NFTs with a superpower to challenges you join and multiply your XP or coins. Beware, this is not pay-to-win since you only get more XP; it's not helping you to get a higher score.

PLAYER LIMIT
From now some challenges are going to have a player limit per team. You will only be able to line up a few players from each available team but not all of one team.

Besides that, we have a lot of fixes again in the background to improve your experience.
